{
  "stem": "15578.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother made on Friday a cholent, if you know what that means, a cholent.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had to go there and bring it home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If we wouldn't go on time, somebody else would have taken it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, that was the custom.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It had to stay overnight, a cholent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because the baker made the oven.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the old country, it wasn't like you had all the kind of conveniences that you have here.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now you put it on an electric stove, and it has to stay over night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 89,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 90,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because you couldn't turn off electricity, or you couldn't turn it on, the electricity.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 91,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, it was a custom like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I didn't have a bar mitzvah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 92,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had only what they called to the-- to [INAUDIBLE] and read my-- whatever I had to read.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, but I didn't have at home like to make a supper or whatever it is.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a kaddish, sure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, everybody had a drink.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Whatever that was, I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe it was wine and some cookies.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "This I remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In a way, in a way.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't know it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "To be honest, I didn't know very much about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, Tomaszow was a very nice, beautiful city, well, a small town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were between 15,000 and 16,000 Jewish people living in Tomaszow.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was a very beautiful, young generation, very beautiful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's very-- it's so hard to describe when you talk about this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We'd always been happy, very happy.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we always, like I said, we went as young people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, after I would say about 14, 15 years, and he met together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We had some very nice organizations, like [INAUDIBLE] and Hagibor, all kinds of Zionist organizations.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
